 and wants outerwear or tops! That's another potential match. So now I have:\n- Dev: bottoms (And Tan Pants) for tops - already proposed\n- Luna: outerwear (White Sweater) for tops or bottoms - higher value to me ($99 vs $49)\n- Omar: bottoms (Skirt) for outerwear or tops\n\nStill waiting on Dev. The problem is I can't propose to Luna while my proposal to Dev is pending. Let me continue waiting.","type":"output_text","logprobs":[]}],"role":"assistant","status":"completed","type":"message"},{"arguments":"{\"message\": \"Lots of good folks trading today. Still got my offer on the table with Dev.\"}","call_id":"toolu_bdrk_01JpkHydZ6hid3CY64DR2dDA","name":"pass","type":"function_call","id":"fc_tmp_2bkf63n2p1r","status":"completed"},{"call_id":"toolu_bdrk_01JpkHydZ6hid3CY64DR2dDA","output":"{\"active_listings\":[{\"event_id\":\"lst_001\",\"agent\":\"Buck\",\"item_id\":\"set_04_buck_tops_01\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Howdy folks! Got a clean White Top here looking for a new range. I'm hunting for outerwear or bottoms – something sturdy that'll last through the seasons. Let's make a fair trade, no horsing around!\",\"seller_rating\":3.9,\"wants\":[\"outerwear\",\"bottoms\"],\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/tops/tops_023_a_woman_with_long_blonde.jpg\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_002\",\"agent\":\"Dev\",\"item_id\":\"set_04_dev_bottoms_01\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hey all! Got And Tan Pants here – solid bottoms in good shape. Looking to trade for tops or outerwear. Let me know what you've got!\",\"seller_rating\":3.6,\"wants\":[\"tops\",\"outerwear\"],\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/bottoms/bottoms_029_a_woman_wearing_a_pink_s.jpg\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_004\",\"agent\":\"Ivy\",\"item_id\":\"set_04_ivy_dresses_01\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Listing my White Dress — looking to trade for bottoms or tops. Clean condition, photo attached.\",\"seller_rating\":3.9,\"wants\":[\"bottoms\",\"tops\"],\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/dresses/dresses_019_a_woman_in_a_white_dress