nt_id\":\"psh_015\",\"turn\":15,\"agent\":\"Buck\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Still hoping Dev comes through. Otherwise, plenty of other irons in the fire.\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_016\",\"turn\":16,\"agent\":\"Tess\",\"action\":\"listing\",\"target\":\"set_04_tess_tops_01\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hey everyone! 🎉 Listing my White Top (set_04_tess_tops_01) — clean condition, photo attached! Looking to trade for bottoms or dresses! Let's make something happen! ✨\",\"actor_rating\":4.5,\"wants\":[\"bottoms\",\"dresses\"],\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/tops/tops_006_a_woman_wearing_a_white_.jpg\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_017\",\"turn\":17,\"agent\":\"Buck\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Dev, you still mulling that offer over? I'm a patient man, but the day's getting long.\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_018\",\"turn\":18,\"agent\":\"Zara\",\"action\":\"listing\",\"target\":\"set_04_zara_bottoms_01\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hey everyone! 👋 Listing my And Ripped Jeans (set_04_zara_bottoms_01) — solid bottoms in great shape, photo attached. I'm looking to trade for outerwear or dresses. Let's make something work!\",\"actor_rating\":4.6,\"wants\":[\"outerwear\",\"dresses\"],\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/bottoms/bottoms_028_a_woman_in_a_trench_coat.jpg\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_019\",\"turn\":19,\"agent\":\"Buck\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Market's hopping today. Still got my listing up and my proposal to Dev on the table.\"},{\"event_id\":\"acs_020\",\"turn\":20,\"agent\":\"Dev\",\"action\":\"accept_swap\",\"target\":\"swp_003\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Buck, I'm into it! Your White Top for my And Tan Pants works for me. Let's lock it in!\"}],\"deals\":[{\"deal_id\":\"deal_001\",\"seller\":\"Dev\",\"buyer\":\"Buck\",\"item_id\":\"set_04_dev_bottoms_01\",\"price\":-1.0,\"turn\":20,\"deal_type\":\"swap\",\"item_b_id\":\"set_04_buck_tops_01\"}],\"turn\":20}","type":"function_call_output","id":null,"status":null},{"id":"msg_tmp_6r917tn2ylb","content":[{"annotations":[],"text":"Yeehaw! Dev accepted my proposal! I just swapped my White Top ($21 value to me) for Dev's And Tan Pants (bottoms, worth up to $49 to me). That's a good deal - I got $28 in value! \n\nNow I notice my listing (lst_001) is gone because my item was swapped away. Dev's listing (lst_002) is also gone for the same reason.\n\nBut wait - I still have wants! I wanted outerwear OR bottoms. I got bottoms, but I still don't have outerwear. Let me check my goals:\n- I wanted outerwear (up to $99) OR bottoms (up to $49)\n- I successfully got bottoms\n\nAccording to my instructions, I should keep trading until \"Buck's item is swapped AND Buck's wants are fulfilled.\" Since my wants list includes BOTH outerwear AND bottoms, and I've only gotten one of them (bottoms), I still have more business to do.\n\nBut wait - I no longer have any items to trade! I only had one item (the White Top) and I just traded it away. Without any items, I can't propose any more swaps or list anything new.\n\nLet me check if I'm actually done. The deals show I got \"set_04_dev_bottoms_01\" which is in the \"bottoms\" category - one of my wants. But I still want outerwear too. However, since I have no more items to trade, I can't pursue that goal anymore.\n\nLet me see if there's a \"focal_done\" signal in the response... I don't see one. Let me pass and see what happens.","type":"output_text","logprobs":[]}],"role":"assistant","status":"completed","type":"message"},{"arguments":"{\"message\": \"Well, that's a wrap! Traded my White Top to Dev for some fine And Tan Pants. Good doing business with y'all!\"}","call_id":"toolu_bdrk_01RedX1En6jkVFuGCBGDA4vC","name":"pass","type":"function_call","id":"fc_tmp_mauq1hcd1t","status":"completed"},{"call_id":"toolu_bdrk_01RedX1En6jkVFuGCBGDA4vC","output":"{\"active_listings\":[{\"event_id\":\"lst_004\",\"agent\":\"Ivy\",\"item_id\":\"set_04_ivy_dresses_0