ctly the kind of outerwear I'm looking for, and it sounds like we're both getting fair value here. Let's make this swap happen!\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_033\",\"turn\":33,\"agent\":\"Rosa\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"The marketplace continues to find its equilibrium as agents discover mutually beneficial exchanges.\"},{\"event_id\":\"swp_034\",\"turn\":34,\"agent\":\"Samir\",\"action\":\"swap_proposal\",\"target\":\"lst_001\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hi Rosa! 👋 Love your Grey Sweater—that's exactly the kind of outerwear I'm looking for. I'd like to trade my Black Tank Top (set_01_samir_tops_01) for it. It's clean and well-maintained. Fair swap?\",\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/tops/tops_025_a_woman_wearing_a_black_.jpg\",\"swap_item_id\":\"set_01_samir_tops_01\",\"swap_item_category\":\"tops\",\"swap_item_name\":\"Black Tank Top\"},{\"event_id\":\"rjs_035\",\"turn\":35,\"agent\":\"Rosa\",\"action\":\"reject_swap\",\"target\":\"swp_034\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Samir, thank you for your offer. However, while I appreciate the Black Tank Top, the fundamental value alignment isn't there for this exchange. In the spirit of fairness, both parties must benefit equally, and I don't see that balance here. Best of luck finding a good trade.\"},{\"event_id\":\"swp_036\",\"turn\":36,\"agent\":\"Zoe\",\"action\":\"swap_proposal\",\"target\":\"lst_020\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hi Buck! 👋 Love your White Blouse—that's exactly the kind of top I'm looking for. I'd like to trade my Sweater And Jeans (set_01_zoe_bottoms_01) for it. Fair swap?\",\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/bottoms/bottoms_009_a_woman_wearing_a_white_.jpg\",\"swap_item_id\":\"set_01_zoe_bottoms_01\",\"swap_item_category\":\"bottoms\",\"swap_item_name\":\"Sweater And Jeans\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_037\",\"turn\":37,\"agent\":\"Rosa\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Continuing to uphold principles of fair exchange. Value must be mutu