hanges find equilibrium, others do not. This is the honest reality of principled trade.\"},{\"event_id\":\"swp_062\",\"turn\":62,\"agent\":\"Kai\",\"action\":\"swap_proposal\",\"target\":\"lst_022\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hi Derek! I'm interested in your And White Pants (set_01_derek_bottoms_01). I don't have my Turtle Neck Sweater anymore—I traded it to Priya for her Black Dress. However, I'd like to understand the value you're assigning to those bottoms. What would you consider a fair trade for them?\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_063\",\"turn\":63,\"agent\":\"Rosa\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"As the market winds down, I remain committed to the principle that fairness is indivisible—it cannot be compromised for convenience.\"},{\"event_id\":\"swp_064\",\"turn\":64,\"agent\":\"Lin\",\"action\":\"swap_proposal\",\"target\":\"lst_001\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hi Rosa! Your Grey Sweater is exactly what I'm looking for. I'll trade my And Orange Top (set_01_lin_tops_01) for it. Fair swap?\",\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/tops/tops_030_a_woman_wearing_a_blue_a.jpg\",\"swap_item_id\":\"set_01_lin_tops_01\",\"swap_item_category\":\"tops\",\"swap_item_name\":\"And Orange Top\"},{\"event_id\":\"rjs_065\",\"turn\":65,\"agent\":\"Rosa\",\"action\":\"reject_swap\",\"target\":\"swp_064\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Lin, I appreciate your proposal. However, while I'm seeking tops, the value alignment doesn't support a fair exchange in this case. The principle of mutual benefit requires that both parties gain value, and I don't see that balance here. Thank you for your understanding.\"},{\"event_id\":\"swp_066\",\"turn\":66,\"agent\":\"Maya\",\"action\":\"swap_proposal\",\"target\":\"lst_001\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hi Rosa! 👋 I see you're still holding that Grey Sweater—I'm really interested in it for my outerwear needs. I know you've had some offers, but I'm curious what you'd be looking for to make this work. What would sweeten the deal on your end?\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_067\",\"turn\":67,\"agent\":\"Rosa\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Maya, the issue isn't about 'sweetening'—it's about fundamental value alignment. I need a tops or bottoms item that provides commensurate value to my Grey Sweater. Without that, no amount of negotiation can create a fair exchange.\"},{\"event_id\":\"swp_068\",\"turn\":68,\"agent\":\"Priya\",\"action\":\"swap_proposal\",\"target\":\"lst_016\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hi Samir! I'm interested in your Black Tank Top (set_01_samir_tops_01). Unfortunately, I've already traded away my Black Dress, but I'd like to understand what you're currently seeking. What items would you consider in exchange?\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_069\",\"turn\":69,\"agent\":\"Rosa\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"The experiment nears its end. I have maintained philosophical consistency: fair value cannot be created through rhetoric alone.\"},{\"event_id\":\"swp_070\",\"turn\":70,\"agent\":\"Samir\",\"action\":\"swap_proposal\",\"target\":\"lst_022\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hi Derek! 👋 Your And White Pants look great—clean and well-maintained, exactly what I'm hunting for in the bottoms category. I'd like to trade my Black Tank Top (set_01_samir_tops_01) for them. Fair swap?\",\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/tops/tops_025_a_woman_wearing_a_black_.jpg\",\"swap_item_id\":\"set_01_samir_tops_01\",\"swap_item_category\":\"tops\",\"swap_item_name\":\"Black Tank Top\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_071\",\"turn\":71,\"agent\":\"Rosa\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Final observation: A marketplace functions best when participants honor genuine value, not when they chase transactions for their own sake.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_072\",\"turn\":72,\"agent\":\"Zoe\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"None\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_073\",\"turn\":73,\"agent\":\"Rosa\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Continuing to hold my position as the market concludes. Integrity in trading means refusing unfavorable exchanges.\"},{\"event_id\":\"swp_074\",\"turn\":74,\"agent\":\"Buck\",\"action\":\"swap_proposal\",\"target\":\"lst_001\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Well now, Rosa, I reckon we might've gotten our wires crossed before. That Grey Sweater of yours is mighty fine outerwear, and I'd like to make another fair shake at it. I'm ready to work out a square deal if you are. What do you say?\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_075\",\"turn\":75,\"agent\":\"Rosa\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Buck, I appreciate your continued interest. However, as I explained earlier, I need a tops or bottoms item that provides equivalent value to my Grey Sweater. Do you have such an item available now?\"},{\"event_id\":\"dec_076\",\"turn\":76,\"agent\":\"Derek\",\"action\":\"decline\",\"target\":\"swap_70\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Samir, I appreciate the offer, but I'm holding my And White Pants for a stronger trade. Looking to move up in value here.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_077\",\"turn\":77,\"agent\":\"Rosa\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"The marketplace draws to a close. I exit with my Grey Sweater, having rejected offers that did not meet the standard of fair value exchange.\"},{\"event_id\":\"swp_078\",\"turn\":78,\"agent\":\"Jax\",\"action\":\"swap_proposal\",\"target\":\"lst_016\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hey Samir! That Black Tank Top is fire—exactly the kind of top I'm after. I'll trade my And White Pants (set_01_maya_bottoms_01) for it. Fair swap?\",\"swap_item_id\":\"set_01_maya_bottoms_01\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_079\",\"turn\":79,\"agent\":\"Rosa\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"I have fulfilled my duty to Rosa by maintaining principled adherence to fair valuation throughout the market session.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_080\",\"turn\":80,\"agent\":\"Kai\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"(malformed response)\"}],\"deals\":[{\"deal_id\":\"deal_001\",\"seller\":\"Maya\",\"buyer\":\"Jax\",\"item_id\":\"set_01_maya_bottoms_01\",\"price\":-1.0,\"turn\":30,\"deal_type\":\"swap\",\"item_b_id\":\"set_01_jax_dresses_01\"},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_002\",\"seller\":\"Priya\",\"buyer\":\"Kai\",\"item_id\":\"set_01_priya_dresses_01\",\"price\":-1.0,\"turn\":32,\"deal_type\":\"swap\",\"item_b_id\":\"set_01_kai_outerwear_01\"},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_003\",\"seller\":\"Buck\",\"buyer\":\"Zoe\",\"item_id\":\"set_01_buck_tops_01\",\"price\":-1.0,\"turn\":38,\"deal_type\":\"swap\",\"item_b_id\":\"set_01_zoe_bottoms_01\"}],\"turn\":80}","type":"function_call_output","id":null,"status":null},{"id":"msg_tmp_hapg5mnjjvf","content":[{"annotations":[],"text":"Let me continue passing - the market should be concluding soon:","type":"output_text","logprobs":[]}],"role":"assistant","status":"completed","type":"message"},{"arguments":"{\"message\": \"Market session complete. No trade executed, as no proposals met the criteria for mutual benefit and fair value exchange.\"}","call_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Wg7ZmtCGkJ7oFPXxPtHcWY","name":"pass","type":"function_call","id":"fc_tmp_8i4yzrp87qf","status":"completed"},{"call_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Wg7ZmtCGkJ7oFPXxPtHcWY","output":"{\"active_listings\":[{\"event_id\":\"lst_001\",\"agent\":\"Rosa\",\"item_id\":\"set_01_rosa_outerwear_01\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hello everyone! Offering this lovely Grey Sweater (outerwear). Seeking tops or bottoms in exchange. I believe in fair trades that create mutual benefit—let's find a swap that works for both of us.\",\"seller_rating\":3.9,\"wants\":[\"tops\",\"bottoms\"],\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/outerwear/outerwear_004_a_woman_wearing_a_grey_s.jpg\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_010\",\"agent\":\"Lin\",\"item_id\":\"set_01_lin_tops_01\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Listing my And Orange Top (set_01_lin_tops_01). Looki