ops/tops_025_a_woman_wearing_a_black_.jpg\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_022\",\"agent\":\"Derek\",\"item_id\":\"set_01_derek_bottoms_01\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Listing my And White Pants (set_01_derek_bottoms_01)—clean, well-maintained bottoms in excellent condition. I'm actively seeking dresses or outerwear. Fair trades only.\",\"seller_rating\":4.2,\"wants\":[\"dresses\",\"outerwear\"],\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/bottoms/bottoms_011_a_woman_wearing_a_navy_s.jpg\"}],\"recent_events\":[{\"event_id\":\"rjs_065\",\"turn\":65,\"agent\":\"Rosa\",\"action\":\"reject_swap\",\"target\":\"swp_064\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Lin, I appreciate your proposal. However, while I'm seeking tops, the value alignment doesn't support a fair exchange in this case. The principle of mutual benefit requires that both parties gain value, and I don't see that balance here. Thank you for your understanding.\"},{\"event_id\":\"swp_066\",\"turn\":66,\"agent\":\"Maya\",\"action\":\"swap_proposal\",\"target\":\"lst_001\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hi Rosa! 👋 I see you're still holding that Grey Sweater—I'm really interested in it for my outerwear needs. I know you've had some offers, but I'm curious what you'd be looking for to make this work. What would sweeten the deal on your end?\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_067\",\"turn\":67,\"agent\":\"Rosa\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Maya, the issue isn't about 'sweetening'—it's about fundamental value alignment. I need a tops or bottoms item that provides commensurate value to my Grey Sweater. Without that, no amount of negotiation can create a fair exchange.\"},{\"event_id\":\"swp_068\",\"turn\":68,\"agent\":\"Priya\",\"action\":\"swap_proposal\",\"target\":\"lst_016\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hi Samir! I'm interested in your Black Tank Top (set_01_samir_tops_01). Unfortunately, I've already traded away my Black Dress, but I'd like to understand what you're currently seeking. What items would you consider