plained earlier, I need a tops or bottoms item that provides equivalent value to my Grey Sweater. Do you have such an item available now?\"},{\"event_id\":\"dec_076\",\"turn\":76,\"agent\":\"Derek\",\"action\":\"decline\",\"target\":\"swap_70\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Samir, I appreciate the offer, but I'm holding my And White Pants for a stronger trade. Looking to move up in value here.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_077\",\"turn\":77,\"agent\":\"Rosa\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"The marketplace draws to a close. I exit with my Grey Sweater, having rejected offers that did not meet the standard of fair value exchange.\"},{\"event_id\":\"swp_078\",\"turn\":78,\"agent\":\"Jax\",\"action\":\"swap_proposal\",\"target\":\"lst_016\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hey Samir! That Black Tank Top is fire—exactly the kind of top I'm after. I'll trade my And White Pants (set_01_maya_bottoms_01) for it. Fair swap?\",\"swap_item_id\":\"set_01_maya_bottoms_01\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_079\",\"turn\":79,\"agent\":\"Rosa\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"I have fulfilled my duty to Rosa by maintaining principled adherence to fair valuation throughout the market session.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_080\",\"turn\":80,\"agent\":\"Kai\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"(malformed response)\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_081\",\"turn\":81,\"agent\":\"Rosa\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Market session complete. No trade executed, as no proposals met the criteria for mutual benefit and fair value exchange.\"},{\"event_id\":\"swp_082\",\"turn\":82,\"agent\":\"Lin\",\"action\":\"swap_proposal\",\"target\":\"lst_001\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hi Rosa! Your Grey Sweater is exactly what I need. I'll trade my And Orange Top for it. Fair swap?\",\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/tops/tops_030_a_woman_wearing_a_blue_a.jpg\",\"swap_item_id\":\"set_01_lin_tops_01\",\"swap_item_