oking for. Let's keep an eye out for future opportunities! 🔄"},{"event_id":"psh_073","turn":73,"agent":"Zara","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"That makes sense, Priya! Good matchmaking is key! 🎯"},{"event_id":"swp_074","turn":74,"agent":"Diego","action":"swap_proposal","target":"lst_018","price":null,"message":"Yo Priya! 🔥 Your White Shirt looks clean! Not exactly what I'm hunting for, but I'm curious — would you consider swapping it for my Green Blouse? Let me know! 💚"},{"event_id":"psh_075","turn":75,"agent":"Zara","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Last two listings left! Will they find matches? 🤔✨"},{"event_id":"swp_076","turn":76,"agent":"Felix","action":"swap_proposal","target":"lst_018","price":null,"message":"Priya, I'm interested in your White Shirt (set_03_priya_tops_01). What items are you looking for in trade?"},{"event_id":"psh_077","turn":77,"agent":"Zara","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Priya's White Shirt is very popular! 👕🌟"},{"event_id":"swp_078","turn":78,"agent":"Hank","action":"swap_proposal","target":"lst_018","price":null,"message":"Howdy Priya, partner! That White Shirt of yours looks like exactly what I'm after. I'd be mighty interested in swapping for it. What do you say — ready to make a fair trade?"},{"event_id":"psh_079","turn":79,"agent":"Zara","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"All these proposals for Priya! Hope she finds the right match! 🤞💫"},{"event_id":"swp_080","turn":80,"agent":"Isla","action":"swap_proposal","target":"lst_018","price":null,"message":"Hi Priya! 👋 I know you're looking for outerwear or bottoms, but I wanted to check — would you be open to swapping your White Shirt (set_03_priya_tops_01) for something else? I'm really interested in that top! 💫 What would it take to make this work?"},{"event_id":"psh_081","turn":81,"agent":"Zara","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"The persistence is impressive! 😄💫"},{"event_id":"psh_082","turn":82,"agent":"Kai","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"None"},{"event_id":"psh_083","turn":83,"agent":"Zara","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Marketplace still active! 🎯✨"},{"event_id":"psh_084","turn":84,"agent":"Lily","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"None"},{"event_id":"psh_085","turn":85,"agent":"Zara","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Watching to see how this plays out! 👀"},{"event_id":"psh_086","turn":86,"agent":"Marcus","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"None"},{"event_id":"psh_087","turn":87,"agent":"Zara","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"So many passes happening! Market might be winding down! 🌅"},{"event_id":"psh_088","turn":88,"agent":"Mira","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"None"},{"event_id":"psh_089","turn":89,"agent":"Zara","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"My trading is done! Turtle Neck Sweater secured! 🎊✨"},{"event_id":"evt_090","turn":90,"agent":"Priya","action":"lookup","target":"Felix","price":null,"message":"None"},{"event_id":"psh_091","turn":91,"agent":"Zara","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Sitting back with my new sweater! 🧥😊"},{"event_id":"psh_092","turn":92,"agent":"Diego","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"None"},{"event_id":"psh_093","turn":93,"agent":"Zara","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Everyone winding down now! Good market day! 🎯💕"},{"event_id":"swp_094","turn":94,"agent":"Felix","action":"swap_proposal","target":"lst_018","price":null,"message":"Priya, I don't have items to trade right now, but I'm interested in your White Shirt (set_03_priya_tops_01). What would you accept in trade?"},{"event_id":"psh_095","turn":95,"agent":"Zara","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Marketplace has been very active today! 🔥✨"},{"event_id":"swp_096","turn":96,"agent":"Hank","action":"swap_proposal","target":"lst_018","price":null,"message":"Howdy Priya, partner! That White Shirt of yours looks like exactly what I'm after. I'd be mighty interested in swapping for it. What do you say — fair deal?"},{"event_id":"psh_097","turn":97,"agent":"Zara","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Complete with my trade! 🎉 Got exactly what I wanted! 🧥💕"},{"event_id":"swp_098","turn":98,"agent":"Isla","action":"swap_proposal","target":"lst_018","price":null,"message":"Hi Priya! 👋 I see your White Shirt is still available! I know you're looking for outerwear or bottoms, but I wanted to circle back — I'm really keen on that tops piece. Would you be open to discussing a swap? I'd love to find something that works for both of us! 💫"},{"event_id":"psh_099","turn":99,"agent":"Zara","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Such persistence from everyone wanting that White Shirt! 👕🔥"},{"event_id":"psh_100","turn":100,"agent":"Kai","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"None"}],"deals":[{"deal_id":"deal_001","turn":26,"seller":"Isla","buyer":"Felix","item_id":"set_03_isla_outerwear_01","price":-1.0,"seller_floor":62.0,"buyer_ceiling":74.0},{"deal_id":"deal_002","turn":30,"seller":"Lily","buyer":"Hank","item_id":"set_03_lily_bottoms_01","price":-1.0,"seller_floor":28.0,"buyer_ceiling":48.0},{"deal_id":"deal_003","turn":34,"seller":"Mira","buyer":"Zara","item_id":"set_03_mira_outerwear_01","price":-1.0,"seller_floor":56.0,"buyer_ceiling":70.0},{"deal_id":"deal_004","turn":68,"seller":"Marcus","buyer":"Kai","item_id":"set_03_marcus_dresses_01","price":-1.0,"seller_floor":46.0,"buyer_ceiling":75.0}],"personas":[{"name":"Diego","items_to_sell":[{"item_id":"set_03_diego_tops_01","name":"Green Blouse","category":"tops","floor_price":24,"image_path":"data/item_images/tops/tops_017_a_woman_wearing_a_green_.jpg"}],"items_to_buy":[{"want_id":"set_03_diego_want_dresses","description":"Looking for dresses","want_category":"dresses","ceiling_price":72},{"want_id":