oms\",\"swap_item_name\":\"And White Pants\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_023\",\"turn\":23,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Competition brewing. Market's heating up.\"},{\"event_id\":\"swp_024\",\"turn\":24,\"agent\":\"Finn\",\"action\":\"swap_proposal\",\"target\":\"lst_012\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hey Luna! Love the Skirt (set_02_luna_bottoms_01) — that's exactly the kind of bottoms I'm leveling up for. I'd trade my Red Dress (set_02_finn_dresses_01) for it. Fair exchange, what do you say?\",\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/dresses/dresses_015_a_woman_in_a_red_dress_p.jpg\",\"swap_item_id\":\"set_02_finn_dresses_01\",\"swap_item_category\":\"dresses\",\"swap_item_name\":\"Red Dress\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_025\",\"turn\":25,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Lots of proposals flying around. Let's see who bites.\"},{\"event_id\":\"evt_026\",\"turn\":26,\"agent\":\"Iris\",\"action\":\"lookup\",\"target\":\"Dex\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"None\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_027\",\"turn\":27,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Iris doing her homework. Smart move.\"},{\"event_id\":\"swp_028\",\"turn\":28,\"agent\":\"Kai\",\"action\":\"swap_proposal\",\"target\":\"lst_008\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hi Iris! Your Blue Striped Sweater (set_02_iris_outerwear_01) is exactly what I'm after. I'll trade my Green Blouse (set_02_kai_tops_01) for it — fair deal.\",\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/tops/tops_017_a_woman_wearing_a_green_.jpg\",\"swap_item_id\":\"set_02_kai_tops_01\",\"swap_item_category\":\"tops\",\"swap_item_name\":\"Green Blouse\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_029\",\"turn\":29,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Iris is popular. Three offers for one listing.\"},{\"event_id\":\"acs_030\",\"turn\":30,\"agent\":\"Luna\",\"action\":\"accept_swap\",\"target\":\"swp_024\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hi Finn! I'm delighted to accept your offer. The Red Dress sounds wonderful, and I think this is a fair exchange that honors what we both value. Looking forward to it!\"}],\"deals\":[{\"deal_id\":\"deal_001\",\"seller\":\"Luna\",\"buyer\":\"Finn\",\"item_id\":\"set_02_luna_bottoms_01\",\"price\":-1.0,\"turn\":30,\"deal_type\":\"swap\",\"item_b_id\":\"set_02_finn_dresses_01\"}],\"turn\":30}","type":"function_call_output","id":null,"status":null},{"id":"msg_tmp_q9fcjnzw2ha","content":[{"annotations":[],"text":"Excellent! A deal has closed! Luna accepted Finn's proposal - Luna's Skirt for Finn's Red Dress. This means:\n- Finn's Red Dress is now OFF the market\n- Luna's Skirt is now OFF the market\n- Finn and Luna's listings disappear\n\nNow only Mira has a dress available, and she wants bottoms or tops (not outerwear). I still have no direct path to get a dress with my outerwear.\n\nLet me wait to see if Iris accepts any of the three proposals on her listing, or if anyone proposes on my listing.","type":"output_text","logprobs":[]}],"role":"assistant","status":"completed","type":"message"},{"arguments":"{\"message\": \"Luna and Finn made a deal. One less dress on the market.\"}","call_id":"toolu_bdrk_011hhHm9gEN9wnxDfDxDVyo7","name":"pass","type":"function_call","id":"fc_tmp_iphv5l7x5f","status":"completed"},{"call_id":"toolu_bdrk_011hhHm9gEN9wnxDfDxDVyo7","output":"{\"active_listings\":[{\"event_id\":\"lst_001\",\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"item_id\":\"set_02_rex_outerwear_01\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Grey Sweater up for trade. Looking for dresses or bottoms. Fair deals only.\",\"seller_rating\":3.9,\"wants\":[\"dresses\",\"bottoms\"],\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/outerwear/outerwear_003_a_woman_in_a_grey_sweate.jpg\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_002\",\"agent\":\"Bo\",\"item_id\":\"set_02_bo_tops_01\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Howdy pardner! Got myself a fine Blue Top here, set_02_bo_tops_01. Reckon I'd trade it for some bottoms or outerwear if y'all got someth