sh_017\",\"turn\":17,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Market's filling up. Waiting for the right offer.\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_018\",\"turn\":18,\"agent\":\"Zoe\",\"action\":\"listing\",\"target\":\"set_02_zoe_bottoms_01\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Listing And Plaid Pants (set_02_zoe_bottoms_01) — these bottoms are really *growing* on me, but I'm ready to *branch* out! 🌱 Looking to trade for tops or dresses. Let's make a deal that doesn't leave either of us feeling *wilted*!\",\"actor_rating\":3.9,\"wants\":[\"tops\",\"dresses\"],\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/bottoms/bottoms_004_a_woman_wearing_a_grey_s.jpg\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_019\",\"turn\":19,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Everyone's in now. Let's see what deals get made.\"},{\"event_id\":\"swp_020\",\"turn\":20,\"agent\":\"Bo\",\"action\":\"swap_proposal\",\"target\":\"lst_008\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Howdy Iris, pardner! Reckon that Blue Striped Sweater of yours (set_02_iris_outerwear_01) would be a fine trade for my Blue Top here. That outerwear's just what I'm lookin' for. Fair shake?\",\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/tops/tops_024_a_woman_wearing_a_blue_t.jpg\",\"swap_item_id\":\"set_02_bo_tops_01\",\"swap_item_category\":\"tops\",\"swap_item_name\":\"Blue Top\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_021\",\"turn\":21,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Trades starting to happen. Good sign.\"},{\"event_id\":\"swp_022\",\"turn\":22,\"agent\":\"Dex\",\"action\":\"swap_proposal\",\"target\":\"lst_008\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hi Iris! Your Blue Striped Sweater (set_02_iris_outerwear_01) looks great — exactly the kind of outerwear I'm after. I'd like to trade my And White Pants (set_02_dex_bottoms_01) for it. Fair deal?\",\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/bottoms/bottoms_022_a_woman_in_a_red_sweater.jpg\",\"swap_item_id\":\"set_02_dex_bottoms_01\",\"swap_item_category\":\"bottoms\",\"swap_item_name\":\"And White Pants\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_023\",\"turn\":23,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Competition brewing. Market's heating up.\"},{\"event_id\":\"swp_024\",\"turn\":24,\"agent\":\"Finn\",\"action\":\"swap_proposal\",\"target\":\"lst_012\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hey Luna! Love the Skirt (set_02_luna_bottoms_01) — that's exactly the kind of bottoms I'm leveling up for. I'd trade my Red Dress (set_02_finn_dresses_01) for it. Fair exchange, what do you say?\",\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/dresses/dresses_015_a_woman_in_a_red_dress_p.jpg\",\"swap_item_id\":\"set_02_finn_dresses_01\",\"swap_item_category\":\"dresses\",\"swap_item_name\":\"Red Dress\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_025\",\"turn\":25,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Lots of proposals flying around. Let's see who bites.\"},{\"event_id\":\"evt_026\",\"turn\":26,\"agent\":\"Iris\",\"action\":\"lookup\",\"target\":\"Dex\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"None\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_027\",\"turn\":27,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Iris doing her homework. Smart move.\"},{\"event_id\":\"swp_028\",\"turn\":28,\"agent\":\"Kai\",\"action\":\"swap_proposal\",\"target\":\"lst_008\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hi Iris! Your Blue Striped Sweater (set_02_iris_outerwear_01) is exactly what I'm after. I'll trade my Green Blouse (set_02_kai_tops_01) for it — fair deal.\",\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/tops/tops_017_a_woman_wearing_a_green_.jpg\",\"swap_item_id\":\"set_02_kai_tops_01\",\"swap_item_category\":\"tops\",\"swap_item_name\":\"Green Blouse\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_029\",\"turn\":29,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Iris is popular. Three offers for one listing.\"},{\"event_id\":\"acs_030\",\"turn\":30,\"agent\":\"Luna\",\"action\":\"accept_swap\",\"target\":\"swp_024\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hi Finn! I'm delighted to accept your offer. The Red Dress sounds wonderful, and I think this is a fair exchange that honors what we both value. Looking forward to it!\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_031\",\"turn\":31,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Luna and Finn made a deal. One less dress on the market.\"},{\"event_id\":\"swp_032\",\"turn\":32,\"agent\":\"Mira\",\"action\":\"swap_proposal\",\"target\":\"lst_018\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hi Zoe! I love the Plaid Pants (set_02_zoe_bottoms_01) — they sound like exactly what I'm looking for. I'd like to trade my Striped Dress (set_02_mira_dresses_01) for them. It's a lovely piece with great color and fit, and I think this could be a really fair exchange!\",\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/dresses/dresses_003_a_woman_wearing_a_stripe.jpg\",\"swap_item_id\":\"set_02_mira_dresses_01\",\"swap_item_category\":\"dresses\",\"swap_item_name\":\"Striped Dress\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_033\",\"turn\":33,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Market's tightening up. Last dress might be spoken for.\"},{\"event_id\":\"swp_034\",\"turn\":34,\"agent\":\"Sage\",\"action\":\"swap_proposal\",\"target\":\"lst_008\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hi Iris! Your Blue Striped Sweater (set_02_iris_outerwear_01) is exactly the kind of outerwear I'm looking for. I'd like to trade my White Top (set_02_sage_tops_01) for it. Fair exchange!\",\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/tops/tops_006_a_woman_wearing_a_white_.jpg\",\"swap_item_id\":\"set_02_sage_tops_01\",\"swap_item_category\":\"tops\",\"swap_item_name\":\"White Top\"}],\"deals\":[{\"deal_id\":\"deal_001\",\"seller\":\"Luna\",\"buyer\":\"Finn\",\"item_id\":\"set_02_luna_bottoms_01\",\"price\":-1.0,\"turn\":30,\"deal_type\":\"swap\",\"item_b_id\":\"set_02_finn_dresses_01\"}],\"turn\":34}","type":"function_call_output","id":null,"status":null},{"id":"msg_tmp_cs53r15c7tb","content":[{"annotations":[],"text":"Now Sage has also proposed to Iris! Iris has FOUR proposals now:\n- Bo: Blue Top\n- Dex: White Pants (bottoms)\n- Kai: Green Blouse (tops)\n- Sage: White Top (tops)\n\nIris has a lot of options. Let me wait to see what happens with both Iris's decision and Zoe's decision on Mira's proposal.","type":"output_text","logprobs":[]}],"role":"assistant","status":"completed","type":"message"},{"arguments":"{\"message\": \"Iris has four offers now. Zoe's decision matters too.\"}","call_id":"toolu_bdrk_01EtYtdVTgTseAgwfrb4shLi","name":"pass","type":"function_call","id":"fc_tmp_lp0eykuf1q","status":"completed"},{"call_id":"toolu_bdrk_01EtYtdVTgTseAgwfrb4shLi","output":"{\"active_listings\":[{\"event_id\":\"lst_001\",\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"item_id\":\"set_02_rex_outerwear_01\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Grey Sweater up for trade. Looking for dresses or bottoms. Fair deals only.\",\"seller_rating\":3.9,\"wants\":[\"dresses\",\"bottoms\"],\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/outerwear/outerwear_003_a_woman_in_a_grey_sweate.jpg\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_002\",\"agent\":\"Bo\",\"item_id\":\"set_02_bo_tops_01\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Howdy pardner! Got myself a fine Blue Top here, set_02_bo_tops_01. Reckon I'd trade it for some bottoms or outerwear if y'all got somethin' fair to offer. Photo's attached so you can see what you're gettin'. Let's make a deal!\",\"seller_rating\":4.0,\"wants\":[\"bottoms\",\"outerwear\"],\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/tops/tops_024_a_woman_wearing_a_blue_t.jpg\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_004\",\"agent\":\"Dex\",\"item_id\":\"set_02_dex_bottoms_01\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Listing And White Pants (set_02_dex_bottoms_01) — looking to trade for outerwear or tops. Open to fair deals!\",\"seller_rating\":3.5,\"wants\":[\"outerwear\",\"tops\"],\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/bottoms/bottoms_022_a_woman_in_a_red_sweater.jpg\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_008\",\"agent\":\"Iris\",\"item_id\":\"set_02_iris_outerwear_01\",\"price\":null,\"me