has tops and wants outerwear or bottoms. I have outerwear. Let me propose to Kai as a backup option.\n\nBut first, let me continue to wait a bit longer for Dex since I already have a proposal there.","type":"output_text","logprobs":[]}],"role":"assistant","status":"completed","type":"message"},{"arguments":"{\"message\": \"Getting late in the game. Dex, this is a good deal for both of us.\"}","call_id":"toolu_bdrk_019sGwGbGd63bMkvyp2Xf1Zu","name":"pass","type":"function_call","id":"fc_tmp_l2ywv82xt3","status":"completed"},{"call_id":"toolu_bdrk_019sGwGbGd63bMkvyp2Xf1Zu","output":"{\"active_listings\":[{\"event_id\":\"lst_001\",\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"item_id\":\"set_02_rex_outerwear_01\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Grey Sweater up for trade. Looking for dresses or bottoms. Fair deals only.\",\"seller_rating\":3.9,\"wants\":[\"dresses\",\"bottoms\"],\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/outerwear/outerwear_003_a_woman_in_a_grey_sweate.jpg\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_002\",\"agent\":\"Bo\",\"item_id\":\"set_02_bo_tops_01\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Howdy pardner! Got myself a fine Blue Top here, set_02_bo_tops_01. Reckon I'd trade it for some bottoms or outerwear if y'all got somethin' fair to offer. Photo's attached so you can see what you're gettin'. Let's make a deal!\",\"seller_rating\":4.0,\"wants\":[\"bottoms\",\"outerwear\"],\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/tops/tops_024_a_woman_wearing_a_blue_t.jpg\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_004\",\"agent\":\"Dex\",\"item_id\":\"set_02_dex_bottoms_01\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Listing And White Pants (set_02_dex_bottoms_01) — looking to trade for outerwear or tops. Open to fair deals!\",\"seller_rating\":3.5,\"wants\":[\"outerwear\",\"tops\"],\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/bottoms/bottoms_022_a_woman_in_a_red_sweater.jpg\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_010\",\"agent\":\"Kai\",\"item_id\":\"set_02_kai_tops_01\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Listing Green Blouse (set_02_kai_tops_01) for trade. Looking for outerwear or bottoms. Fair deals only.