aring_a_blue_t.jpg\",\"swap_item_id\":\"set_02_bo_tops_01\",\"swap_item_category\":\"tops\",\"swap_item_name\":\"Blue Top\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_057\",\"turn\":57,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Bo's in the mix now. Let's see who Dex picks.\"},{\"event_id\":\"dec_058\",\"turn\":58,\"agent\":\"Dex\",\"action\":\"decline\",\"target\":\"swap_56\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Thanks Bo, but I'm looking to trade my bottoms for outerwear or tops that are worth more to me. Your Blue Top is a nice piece, but I'd need something that feels like a step up in value. Open to other offers though!\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_059\",\"turn\":59,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Dex turned down Bo. My offer's still on the table.\"},{\"event_id\":\"swp_060\",\"turn\":60,\"agent\":\"Finn\",\"action\":\"swap_proposal\",\"target\":\"lst_002\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hey Bo! That Blue Top (set_02_bo_tops_01) looks like exactly the kind of gear I need to level up my wardrobe. I'm interested in trading for it — what would you say to a fair exchange?\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_061\",\"turn\":61,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Dex, I'm waiting. Let's close this deal.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_062\",\"turn\":62,\"agent\":\"Iris\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"None\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_063\",\"turn\":63,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Market's winding down. Dex, you and I can still make this work.\"},{\"event_id\":\"acc_064\",\"turn\":64,\"agent\":\"Kai\",\"action\":\"accept\",\"target\":\"swap_28\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hi Iris! I'm accepting your offer. Your Blue Striped Sweater (set_02_iris_outerwear_01) is exactly what I'm after, and this is a fair trade for my Green Blouse (set_02_kai_tops_01). Let's make this happen!\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_065\",\"turn\"