, you and I can still make this work.\"},{\"event_id\":\"acc_064\",\"turn\":64,\"agent\":\"Kai\",\"action\":\"accept\",\"target\":\"swap_28\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hi Iris! I'm accepting your offer. Your Blue Striped Sweater (set_02_iris_outerwear_01) is exactly what I'm after, and this is a fair trade for my Green Blouse (set_02_kai_tops_01). Let's make this happen!\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_065\",\"turn\":65,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Dex, time to decide. Fair deal on the table.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_066\",\"turn\":66,\"agent\":\"Luna\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"(malformed response)\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_067\",\"turn\":67,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Getting late in the game. Dex, this is a good deal for both of us.\"},{\"event_id\":\"swp_068\",\"turn\":68,\"agent\":\"Mira\",\"action\":\"swap_proposal\",\"target\":\"lst_002\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hi Bo! That Blue Top (set_02_bo_tops_01) sounds perfect for what I'm looking for. I'd love to work out a trade if you're interested!\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_069\",\"turn\":69,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Dex, I need an answer. Yes or no.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_070\",\"turn\":70,\"agent\":\"Sage\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"(malformed response)\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_071\",\"turn\":71,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Last call, Dex. After this, I'm out.\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_072\",\"turn\":72,\"agent\":\"Zoe\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"None\"}],\"deals\":[{\"deal_id\":\"deal_001\",\"seller\":\"Luna\",\"buyer\":\"Finn\",\"item_id\":\"set_02_luna_bottoms_01\",\"price\":-1.0,\"turn\":30,\"deal_type\":\"swap\",\"item_b_id\":\"set_02_finn_dresses_01\"},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_002\",\"seller\":\