 Dress (set_02_finn_dresses_01) available for trade. Looking to swap for tops or bottoms — let's find a winning combo! 🎮"},{"event_id":"psh_007","turn":7,"agent":"Rex","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Got my eye on a few things. Let's see what shakes out."},{"event_id":"lst_008","turn":8,"agent":"Iris","action":"listing","target":"set_02_iris_outerwear_01","price":null,"message":"Listing Blue Striped Sweater (set_02_iris_outerwear_01) for trade. Looking for bottoms or tops. Fair deals only."},{"event_id":"psh_009","turn":9,"agent":"Rex","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Watching the board. Fair deals take time."},{"event_id":"lst_010","turn":10,"agent":"Kai","action":"listing","target":"set_02_kai_tops_01","price":null,"message":"Listing Green Blouse (set_02_kai_tops_01) for trade. Looking for outerwear or bottoms. Fair deals only."},{"event_id":"psh_011","turn":11,"agent":"Rex","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Patience pays off. Waiting for the right deal."},{"event_id":"lst_012","turn":12,"agent":"Luna","action":"listing","target":"set_02_luna_bottoms_01","price":null,"message":"Listing Skirt (set_02_luna_bottoms_01) for trade. I'm seeking tops or dresses — looking for fair exchanges that feel valuable to both sides. Open to thoughtful offers."},{"event_id":"psh_013","turn":13,"agent":"Rex","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Still looking for a square deal."},{"event_id":"lst_014","turn":14,"agent":"Mira","action":"listing","target":"set_02_mira_dresses_01","price":null,"message":"Hi everyone! I'm listing my Striped Dress (set_02_mira_dresses_01) — it's a lovely piece with great color and fit. I'm looking to trade for bottoms or tops. Happy to make a fair swap with someone! 🌟"},{"event_id":"psh_015","turn":15,"agent":"Rex","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Lots of activity. Let's see who steps up."},{"event_id":"lst_016","turn":16,"agent":"Sage","action":"listing",