ring bottoms for outerwear. However, this would be an unfavorable trade for me ($45 < $67). But I need to consider: if I don't make a trade, I get nothing. At least with bottoms, I get something I want, even if the value is lower.\n\nLet me wait a bit to see if anyone else posts a dress before considering the unfavorable trade.","type":"output_text","logprobs":[]}],"role":"assistant","status":"completed","type":"message"},{"arguments":"{\"message\": \"Looking for other dress options or favorable trades.\"}","call_id":"toolu_bdrk_015wY5yGcChyFoU2WiVnGLGi","name":"pass","type":"function_call","id":"fc_tmp_z3095wwwlh","status":"completed"},{"call_id":"toolu_bdrk_015wY5yGcChyFoU2WiVnGLGi","output":"{\"active_listings\":[{\"event_id\":\"lst_001\",\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"item_id\":\"set_05_taj_outerwear_01\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Listing my And White Sweater (outerwear). Looking to swap for dresses or bottoms. Open to offers!\",\"seller_rating\":4.0,\"wants\":[\"dresses\",\"bottoms\"],\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/outerwear/outerwear_013_a_woman_wearing_a_pink_a.jpg\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_004\",\"agent\":\"Jade\",\"item_id\":\"set_05_jade_bottoms_01\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Listing my And Tan Pants (set_05_jade_bottoms_01). Looking to swap for tops or dresses. Photo attached. Open to fair trades!\",\"seller_rating\":4.1,\"wants\":[\"tops\",\"dresses\"],\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/bottoms/bottoms_012_a_woman_wearing_a_white_.jpg\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_008\",\"agent\":\"Lin\",\"item_id\":\"set_05_lin_outerwear_01\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Listing my Orange Cardigan Sweater (set_05_lin_outerwear_01). Looking to swap for tops or bottoms. Photo attached. Fair trades welcome.\",\"seller_rating\":4.7,\"wants\":[\"tops\",\"bottoms\"],\"image_path\":\"data/item_images/outerwear/outerwear_008_a_pregnant_woman_wearing.jpg\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_012\",\"agent\":\"Nola\",\"item_id\":\"set_05_nola_bottoms_01\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Listing my Sweater And 